\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

 denote the cyclic permutation 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma\left(\left(a_{1},a_{2},\ldots,a_{p}\right)\right)=\left(a_{2},a_{3},\ldots,a_{p},a_{1}\right)$
\end_inset

.
