\begin_inset Formula $l\mid n$
\end_inset

 then there is a unique subgroup 
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

 of 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

 with 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|H\right|=l$
\end_inset

.
