\begin_layout Proof

\series bold
Existence.

\series default
 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $n=dl$
\end_inset

.
 Then by Theorem 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "orderofg^s-1"

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
