\]

\end_inset

so 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\langle a^{n/l}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

 is a subgroup of 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

 of order 
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

.
