\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "A_nisnormal"

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $A_{n}$
\end_inset

 is a normal subgroup of 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{n}$
\end_inset

 with 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|A_{n}\right|=n!/2$
\end_inset

.
