 is the kernel of the homomorphism sgn of Corollary 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sgnhomomorphism"

\end_inset

.
 By Corollary 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "noevenequalsnoodd"

\end_inset

 the number of even permutations is equal to 
