\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The group 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{n}$
\end_inset

 plays a pivotal role in 
\emph on
Galois Theory
\emph default
, which deals with roots of polynomial equations 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)=0$
\end_inset

 in one variable.
 This theory demonstrates the impossibility of constructing a general algorithm
