Define a map
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f\,\colon\, H\longrightarrow G/K,\ f\left(h\right)=hK.
\]

\end_inset

Note that 
\begin_inset Formula $f\left(a\right)=f\left(b\right)$
\end_inset

 if and only if 
\begin_inset Formula $b^{-1}a\in H\cap K$
\end_inset

.
