[G\,:\, H]\cdot[H\,:\, N] & = & |(G/N)/(H/N)|\cdot[H\,:\, N]\\
 & = & [G/N\,:\, H/N]\cdot[H\,:\, N]\\
 & = & [G/N\,:\, H/N]\cdot|H/N|\\
 & = & |G/N|\qquad(\mathrm{Lagrange's\ Theorem\ \ref{Lagrange})}\\
